decoworld.model.world.safehouse

Class Safehouse

  • java.lang.Object
    • decoworld.model.world.safehouse.Safehouse

  • public class Safehouse
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will handle the safehouses for every player. It will likely be a subclass of an Enterable Building. Invariant: User != null, User is a valid user in the game safehouseLevel != null, safehouseLevel > 1 chest != null, chest contains only non-null items cabinet != null, cabinet contains only non-null achievements
